Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're heading to Mistral?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:00:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they do say the food and\Nwomen are good there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been six months\Nsince the ceasefire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad we both made\Nit through alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand ouvert!\NRead 'em and weep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You've gotta be kidding me!\N- Damn!     - Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! You up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your share of the spoils of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm honored to receive\Nsuch a treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're nice to the trumpeter,\Nyou can hear them sound the retreat better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd to see a new recruit,\Nnow that the draft's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You volunteered?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I wanted to learn\Nhow to play music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An honest girl... I like that!\NGood luck, kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata! Kanata Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3004)}So Ra No Wo To
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sound that Fills the Air -\NThe City of Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize is having a festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't take you further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you've been assigned.\NLocals call it Clocktower Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set a course for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders for Private Kanata Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are ordered to report to the\N1121 Platoon in Seize City, Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helvetia Republic Army HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of 1320, this mission is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of lakes\Nand glass, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to report at 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally let you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direction confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat... A wonderful sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten yen, twenty-five sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful doll-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten had too much fun at the fair,\Nand it ran off in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cats always take their\Ntime getting places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're\Ncute, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were a stray, it'd be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a domesticated cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I found another\Nwonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl from the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Flame Maidens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready... Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have joined them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your uniform's all messy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... A-Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made quite the target...\NCouldn't you have dodged a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NOnce it dries, this dye fades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It comes from a Seize legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend of the Flame Maidens\Nwho protect the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll add it to your tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with the repairs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... This, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That nosy brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Late! Late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's late!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we came to welcome her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's relax and wait for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present from\Nyour father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I get lost a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to that, I met\Nsomeone this wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get lost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell the pitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clear... somehow\Nnostalgic sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd die over something\Nlike that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something\Nto do, so I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell... I'm sure it was\Nreally important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:12:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, before the world\Nbecame the way it is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a winged demon came to live\Nat the bottom of this valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon breathed fire, shook the ground,\Nand caused people to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, he kidnapped the maidens\Nwho lived in the fort,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,locking them in an\Nunderground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls, however,\Nrefused to give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:15:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and called to each other with golden horns\Ngiven to them by the Lord of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon escaping the labyrinth,\Nthey gained the help of an enormous spider
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and defeated the demon, taking its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they'd done so, it began\Nspewing flame everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing had been done, it would have\Nburned the town above to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To keep the flames at bay, the maidens embraced\Nthe demon's head, each in turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, the villagers would throw water\Non the maiden with the flaming head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year passed, and the flames\Ndisappeared at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, every year, the town celebrates\Nthe water-throwing festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to commemorate the maidens\Nwho saved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new girl never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, look at Rio-sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. She looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were right to leave it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we drew straws-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, getting lost means\Nthat something fun happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only when you\Nmeet someone new.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you long for her, she'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sound will always fill the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Fill the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, it reaches\Npeople's ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here sleep the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken now, and embrace the\Ndemon to quell its curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the demon awakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, someone... Hear my sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound fills the air, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kanata Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap out of it, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Clocktower Fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,base camp of the 1121 Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I-I'm very sorry\Nabout yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on,\Ndon't do stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for something as\Nstupid as this bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why we're called\NClocktower Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sound of the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Kazumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you how to\Nplay the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sergeant Rio-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio's fine.
